[[Phylologyl]] yu studhyans testennow ha yethow hen. An hanow yn-tallethvos a styryas kerensa ([[Grekek]] ''philo-'') a studhyans ha bardhonyeth ([[Grekek]] ''-logia''), Phylologyl o onen a'n kensa [[19ves cansvledhen]] nesheans dhe'n yeth denus, mes a ryas forth dhe'n scyens modern [[yethegow]] y'n [[20ves cansvledhen]] avar yndan an scodhyans a [[de Saussure, Ferdinand]] py a argyas fatel an yeth kewsys a goth dhe gafos an plas kensa.

Un scoren phylologyl yu [[yethegow ystorek]]. Hevelepterow ynter [[Sanskrit]] ha'n [[yethow europek]] a vue kensa notyes y'n [[18ves cansvledhen]] avar hag a ledyas dhe'n dyskeverans a [[proto-yndo-europek]]. Bern phylologyl yn yethow hen a hembronkyas dhe'n studhyans a byu y'n [[19ves cansvledhen]] o yethow estranjek rag an golow y a allas tewlel y'n understondyans ha dyskeverans y'n testennow cotha.

Y'n [[USA]], an [[Paper newodhow pupteth phylologyl amerycanek]] a vue fundyes yn [[1880]] gans [[Gildersleeve, Lanneau Basil]] professor orth [[unyversyta John Hopkins]].

